|---|---:|---:|---:|---:|---|
| law_commit_attempt | 4153.041 | 4170.375 | 0.9958 | 64 | one judged Attempt insert per commit under the full law roster (key + containment + window) |
| law_commit_cluster | 4180.125 | 4047.000 | 1.0329 | 256 | one judged 4-row cluster per commit: attempt + verdict + steer + scope — every statement family exercised in one commit |
| law_reject_key | 4219.708 | 3.292 | 1281.8068 | 64 | one REFUSED duplicate-(task, n) commit per sample (Functionality cited) |
